data.description: Immaculate 5 BED plus BONUS nestled in highly desirable Heritage Brook subdivision. The upgraded kitchen includes built-in microwave, gas range w/double ovens, & modern design finishes. The isolated Master Suite boasts full modern bath w/shower & soaking tub, as well as expansive walk-in closet.    Upstairs offers 4th & 5th bedrooms, a full bath, plus huge bonus area! Beautiful built ins and thoughtful floorplan make this home not only perfect for entertaining but also wonderful for everyday easy living. Convenient to Clift Farms and all the amenities Madison has to offer. Come tour 114 Oakside Circle in Madison, Alabama today.
